<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 14:06:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着动荡的投票临近，“选举恐惧”笼罩阿根廷市场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/election-fear-stalks-argentinas-markets-as-volatile-vote-nears/articleshow/104135457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104135457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿根廷即将举行的总统选举给市场带来了不确定性，导致债券下跌和比索暴跌。投资者不确定如何应对激进自由主义候选人哈维尔·米雷(Javier Milei)可能当选，他提出了有利于市场的计划，但也希望关闭央行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 12:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/election-fear-stalks-argentinas-markets-as-volatile-vote-nears/articleshow/104135457.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙国王提名佩德罗·桑切斯竞选首相</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-king-nominates-pedro-sanchez-for-premiership-bid/articleshow/104135115.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104135115.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;下议院议长弗朗西娜·阿门戈尔告诉记者，西班牙国王费利佩周二提名代理首相佩德罗·桑切斯接受议会投票，以决定新的任期，此前他的保守派竞争对手上周未能成为首相。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 12:35:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-king-nominates-pedro-sanchez-for-premiership-bid/articleshow/104135115.cms</guid></item><item><title>“他们只是肉”：俄罗斯将军事和平民罪犯送上战场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/theyre-just-meat-russia-deploys-punishment-battalions-in-echo-of-stalin/articleshow/104132631.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104132631.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据多个消息来源称，被称为“Storm-Z”小队的俄罗斯刑罚部队今年已将数百名军事和民事罪犯送往乌克兰前线，其中包括醉酒的新兵和罪犯。这些隶属于正规军的惩戒小队损失惨重，被俄罗斯国防部视为消耗性步兵。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 11:19:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/theyre-just-meat-russia-deploys-punishment-battalions-in-echo-of-stalin/articleshow/104132631.cms</guid></item><item><title>14岁少年在曼谷商场开枪 造成1死6伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/4-killed-as-14-year-old-opens-fire-at-mall-in-thailands-bangkok/articleshow/104132315.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104132315.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，一名14岁的枪手嫌疑人在泰国首都曼谷的一家豪华购物中心开枪，造成1人死亡、6人受伤。泰国警方已将这名青少年枪手嫌疑人拘留。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 11:12:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/4-killed-as-14-year-old-opens-fire-at-mall-in-thailands-bangkok/articleshow/104132315.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔军政府称袭击加剧，圣战分子杀死 29 名士兵</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigers-junta-says-jihadis-kill-29-soldiers-as-attacks-ramp-up/articleshow/104131354.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104131354.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尼日尔军政府表示，在该国与马里边境附近，至少有 29 名尼日尔士兵被圣战分子杀害，他们正在努力结束一系列袭击。尼日尔国防部长萨利福·莫迪中将在周一晚间的一份声明中表示，100多名极端分子使用自制炸药袭击了部署在边境地区进行清理行动的西非国家安全部队。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigers-junta-says-jihadis-kill-29-soldiers-as-attacks-ramp-up/articleshow/104131354.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其在自杀式炸弹袭击后拘留近千人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-nearly-1000-including-alleged-kurdish-militants-following-suicide-bomb-attack/articleshow/104130697.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130697.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其首都发生自杀式炸弹袭击几天后，警方周二在土耳其各地的突袭中拘留了近千人，其中包括数十名据称与库尔德武装分子有联系的人。周二，警方在土耳其各地逮捕了至少 67 人，目标是涉嫌与库尔德武装分子有联系的人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:31:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-detains-nearly-1000-including-alleged-kurdish-militants-following-suicide-bomb-attack/articleshow/104130697.cms</guid></item><item><title>罗马尼亚决定在学校教授犹太历史和大屠杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/romania-marks-decision-to-teach-jewish-history-holocaust-in-schools/articleshow/104130508.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130508.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;罗马尼亚决定将大屠杀和犹太历史纳入其学校课程。课程改革于 2021 年获得批准，被视为对第二次世界大战期间数十万罗马尼亚和乌克兰犹太人和罗姆人被杀负责的第一步。发起课程改革的立法者西尔维乌·韦克斯勒(Silviu Vexler)表示，该课程是“对所发生的事情完全承担责任的第一个真正的举措”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/romania-marks-decision-to-teach-jewish-history-holocaust-in-schools/articleshow/104130508.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普民事欺诈审判进入第二天，商业帝国岌岌可危</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-civil-fraud-trial-enters-second-day-as-business-empire-hangs-in-balance/articleshow/104130112.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104130112.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普在曼哈顿的民事审判仍在继续，指控他夸大资产价值以获得更优惠的贷款和保险条款。纽约州总检察长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯 (Letitia James) 正在寻求至少 2.5 亿美元的罚款，并永久禁止特朗普及其儿子在纽约经营企业。特朗普否认有不当行为，他的律师表示将上诉。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 10:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-civil-fraud-trial-enters-second-day-as-business-empire-hangs-in-balance/articleshow/104130112.cms</guid></item><item><title>波兰和捷克共和国启动斯洛伐克边境检查以遏制移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/poland-czech-republic-start-slovak-border-checks-to-curb-migration/articleshow/104129028.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104129028.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;波兰和捷克共和国周二表示，他们将在与斯洛伐克的边境进行检查，以遏制日益增长的非法移民。德国上周表示，将加强与波兰和捷克共和国边境的治安，以控制不断上升的非法移民数量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 09:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/poland-czech-republic-start-slovak-border-checks-to-curb-migration/articleshow/104129028.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：伊姆兰·汗的妻子布什拉·比比 (Bushra Bibi) 提出 IHC，担心汗可能在阿迪亚拉监狱“中毒”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-imran-khans-wife-bushra-bibi-moves-ihc-fears-khan-could-be-poisoned-in-adiala-jail/articleshow/104128443.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104128443.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗的妻子布什拉·比比已向伊斯兰堡高等法院提出请求，要求加强阿迪亚拉监狱中丈夫的安全保障。她对他可能中毒表示担忧，并表示他没有获得监狱手册中提到的应有设施。她敦促法院进行干预，确保向汗提供适当的设施、健康的食物和锻炼的权利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 09:38:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-imran-khans-wife-bushra-bibi-moves-ihc-fears-khan-could-be-poisoned-in-adiala-jail/articleshow/104128443.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋在主办联合国气候谈判之前举行大型石油和天然气会议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/uae-holds-major-oil-and-gas-conference-just-ahead-of-hosting-un-climate-talks-in-dubai/articleshow/104128097.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104128097.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;即将举行的联合国第二十八次缔约方会议候任主席苏丹贾比尔敦促石油和天然气公司在应对气候变化方面发挥核心作用。他发出这一呼吁之际，该行业正在增加产量，以利用全球能源价格上涨的机会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 09:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/uae-holds-major-oil-and-gas-conference-just-ahead-of-hosting-un-climate-talks-in-dubai/articleshow/104128097.cms</guid></item><item><title>安卡拉袭击事件后土耳其逮捕了数十人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-arrests-dozens-after-ankara-attack/articleshow/104127138.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104127138.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;安卡拉发生袭击事件后，土耳其逮捕了数十名库尔德武装嫌疑人及其支持者。库尔德工人党声称对这次袭击负责，造成两名警察受伤。土耳其警方击毙了一名袭击者，另一名则在明显的自杀式爆炸中死亡。安全部门已在16个省份拘留了67名“恐怖组织成员”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 08:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-arrests-dozens-after-ankara-attack/articleshow/104127138.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普法官在法庭上微笑、摆出姿势拍照后遭到网上强烈反对</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-judge-faces-online-backlash-after-smiling-posing-for-cameras-in-courtroom/articleshow/104125683.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104125683.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，挑衅的唐纳德·特朗普在审判开始当天对纽约总检察长和主审法官发起了严厉的攻击。司法部长利蒂西亚·詹姆斯正在寻求至少 2.5 亿美元的罚款，永久禁止特朗普及其儿子小唐纳德和埃里克在纽约经营企业，并对特朗普和特朗普集团实施为期五年的商业房地产禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 07:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-judge-faces-online-backlash-after-smiling-posing-for-cameras-in-courtroom/articleshow/104125683.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度敦促世贸组织成员开始基于文本的谈判，寻找公共粮食库存问题的永久解决方案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/india-urges-wto-members-to-start-text-based-talks-on-finding-permanent-solution-to-public-food-stockholding/articleshow/104125060.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104125060.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度呼吁进行基于文本的谈判，以找到世界贸易组织（WTO）粮食安全公共储备问题的永久解决方案。欧盟（EU）已表示愿意讨论该问题。在日内瓦举行的农业谈判会议上讨论了这一话题，欧盟积极回应了有关保障措施和反规避措施的建议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 07:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/india-urges-wto-members-to-start-text-based-talks-on-finding-permanent-solution-to-public-food-stockholding/articleshow/104125060.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国国会议员亨利·奎利亚尔在华盛顿遭劫车</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/henry-cuellar-member-of-us-congress-carjacked-in-washington/articleshow/104122374.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104122374.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据其办公室称，周一晚上，来自德克萨斯州的民主党众议员亨利·奎利亚尔 (Henry Cuellar) 成为三名武装袭击者劫车事件的受害者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 05:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/henry-cuellar-member-of-us-congress-carjacked-in-washington/articleshow/104122374.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普总统任期结束时 13 名联邦处决者的更全面情况浮出水面</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fuller-picture-emerges-of-the-13-federal-executions-at-the-end-of-trumps-presidency/articleshow/104122495.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104122495.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一名德克萨斯州男子因杀害爱荷华州一对 18 岁夫妇而被联邦政府处决，前一天，名人律师艾伦·德肖维茨恳求时任总统唐纳德·特朗普（他的前客户）取消执行死刑。 2020 年 12 月 9 日，德肖维茨给白宫打电话时告诉特朗普，40 岁的布兰登·伯纳德已经不再是 1999 年托德和斯塔西·巴格利被杀时的那个人了，他应该被减刑为无期徒刑在狱中。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 05:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/fuller-picture-emerges-of-the-13-federal-executions-at-the-end-of-trumps-presidency/articleshow/104122495.cms</guid></item><item><title>印尼总统启动中国资助的东南亚第一条高速铁路</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesian-president-launches-southeast-asias-first-high-speed-railway-funded-by-china/articleshow/104118166.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104118166.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度尼西亚总统佐科·维多多周一为东南亚第一条高速铁路揭幕，该铁路即将开始商业运营，这是中国“一带一路”基础设施倡议下的一个关键项目，将大大减少两个主要城市之间的旅行时间。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 02:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indonesian-president-launches-southeast-asias-first-high-speed-railway-funded-by-china/articleshow/104118166.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟寻求保护敏感技术免受中国买家的侵害</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-seeks-to-protect-sensitive-tech-from-chinese-buyers/articleshow/104117478.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104117478.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟将公布一系列敏感技术，这些技术必须不落入中国手中，作为对抗中国侵略性贸易政策的努力的一部分。欧盟委员会将公布一份关键技术清单，如果中国轻易获得这些技术，可能会损害欧盟的安全、利益或人权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 01:51:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-seeks-to-protect-sensitive-tech-from-chinese-buyers/articleshow/104117478.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国登革热疫情：死亡人数突破千人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bangladesh-dengue-outbreak-death-toll-crosses-1000/articleshow/104117346.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104117346.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国正在经历有记录以来最严重的登革热疫情，2023 年前 9 个月报告了 1,000 多人死亡和近 209,000 例感染。在这个人口稠密的国家，医院正在努力应对这种迅速蔓延的疾病。登革热是一种由蚊子传播的疾病，会引起高烧、头痛、恶心，严重时会导致致命的出血。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 01:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bangladesh-dengue-outbreak-death-toll-crosses-1000/articleshow/104117346.cms</guid></item><item><title>委内瑞拉政治反对派拒绝推迟初选的要求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/venezuelas-political-opposition-rejects-request-to-delay-primary/articleshow/104117173.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104117173.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;委内瑞拉反对派选举委员会计划于 10 月下旬继续进行初选，尽管该国全国选举委员会寻求推迟。反对派将面对尼古拉斯·马杜罗总统领导的执政社会主义者，他们目睹了经济崩溃并迫害批评者。虽然马杜罗预计将竞选连任，但他尚未发表正式声明。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 01:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/venezuelas-political-opposition-rejects-request-to-delay-primary/articleshow/104117173.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>